                <h2>
                    Agents that actually <span class="h-word">understand</span> the
                    data.
                </h2>
                <p class="section-sub">
                    After every sync, Dinobase automatically builds a semantic
                    layer. Agents call <code
                        style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.9em;color:var(--green-accent);background:rgba(74,222,128,0.07);padding:0.1rem 0.4rem;border-radius:3px"
